      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know how to explain this but i keep having these intense memories of being in the soviet union in the 30s. like i can actually feel the cold and see the rallies. i think i was actually a high ranking revolutionary leader. it's all coming back to me and it makes so much sense why i feel so disconnected from everything here. it feels like the capitalist system is just a wall built to keep my spirit trapped. do u think its possible for someone to carry that kind of power across lifetimes?",
